{"search_data": "HaryanaHaryana Police HarSamay Citizen Portal \u2013 Digital Signatures In Verification Certificates IntegratedHaryana Police starts HarSamay Citizen Portal at harsamay.gov.in, make registration / login, get character / tenant / police clearance certificate at home, digital signatures integrated with police verification certificates under Harsamay citizen services \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Haryana Police HarSamay Citizen PortalAt this portal, people can apply online to get Police Verification Certificates at their home. As a first step, the functionality of downloading digitally signed character certificate, tenant certificate and police clearance certificate from Haryana Police HarSamay citizen portal would be made available to the people. The state govt. will also integrate other verification services like Employee Verification, Domestic Help Verification, Threat Verification with digital signature. Haryana Home Minister Anil Vij has launched Haryana Police HarSamay Citizen Portal.The portal can now be accessed using the link harsamay.gov.inAt the homepage, click at the \u201cCreate Citizen Login\u201d link as shown below:-Haryana Police Harsamay Portal Citizen LoginThe Haryana Police Harsamay Citizen Registration Form will appear as shown below:-Haryana Police Harsamay Citizen Registration FormHere candidates can enter personal details, address, login details and click at the \u201cSubmit\u201d button to complete the registration process for citizens at the Harsamay Citizen portal of Haryana Police.People can then make login into the HarSamay citizen portal and can even download digitally signed verification certificates from anywhere as per their convenience.Earlier, people had to visit the SP office of their respective districts to collect signed certificates in person. With this change, people can avail delivery of digitally signed certificates directly from the HarSamay portal.Furthermore, police can now complete the entire verification process from their end and make digitally signed certificate available in HarSamay portal. Citizens can log-in and download certificates as per time and place of their convenience.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/have-verification-certificate-while-sitting-at-home-haryana-home-minister-launches-app/articleshow/74102945.cms  at  "}